#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.63"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.63:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.63:0.2"
msgid "7. Saññāvagga"
msgstr "7. Perceptions"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.63:0.3"
msgid "63. Paṭhamavaḍḍhisutta"
msgstr "63. Growth (1st)"

# Unusual use of kāya here. BB has “of this life”, while Thanissaro has “in the body” and Hare has “whole being”. The term coordinates with idheva attano in the verses.
#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.63:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, vaḍḍhīhi vaḍḍhamāno ariyasāvako ariyāya vaḍḍhiyā "
"vaḍḍhati, sārādāyī ca hoti varādāyī ca kāyassa."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a male noble disciple who grows in five ways grows nobly, "
"taking on what is essential and excellent in this life."

msgctxt "an5.63:1.2"
msgid "Katamāhi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.63:1.3"
msgid ""
"Saddhāya vaḍḍhati, sīlena vaḍḍhati, sutena vaḍḍhati, cāgena vaḍḍhati, "
"paññāya vaḍḍhati—"
msgstr "He grows in faith, ethics, learning, generosity, and wisdom."

msgctxt "an5.63:1.4"
msgid ""
"imāhi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi vaḍḍhīhi vaḍḍhamāno ariyasāvako ariyāya "
"vaḍḍhiyā vaḍḍhati, sārādāyī ca hoti varādāyī ca kāyassā”ti."
msgstr ""
"A male noble disciple who grows in these five ways grows nobly, taking on "
"what is essential and excellent in this life."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: ca yo pavaḍḍhati → yodha vaḍḍhati (bj)
msgctxt "an5.63:2.1"
msgid "“Saddhāya sīlena ca yo pavaḍḍhati,"
msgstr "He who grows in faith and ethics,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.63:2.2"
msgid "Paññāya cāgena sutena cūbhayaṃ;"
msgstr "wisdom, and both generosity and learning—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.63:2.3"
msgid "So tādiso sappuriso vicakkhaṇo,"
msgstr "a good man such as he sees clearly,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.63:2.4"
msgid "Ādīyatī sāramidheva attano”ti."
msgstr "and takes on what is essential for himself in this life.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.63:2.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
